# aperysConstant

- _aperysConstant(n)_

Apéry’s constant,
ζ(3),
the infinite sum of the reciprocals of the positive integers, cube.

```
>>> 1.aperysConstant
1.20206

>>> zeta(3)
1.aperysConstant
```

